'''Grree L'Tharr''' was a charming and infamous felinoid [[Jediboh Opera]] actress in the [[Tantrellius Theatre Groupe]]. When a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] came to the ''[[Two Jedi Men From Baronis]]'' play looking for a [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]], they met her backstage. She quickly became fixated on a [[Gender/Legends|male]] member of the group and soon emitted pheromones as all members of her race could do to attract him to her. Soon afterwards, when Grree's best friend [[Plum Tantrellius]] was kidnapped, she joined the group to help them rescue her.

